{"tid":279703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄭已完]明報宣判泰博死刑！","createTime":"2017-06-11T13:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T10:39:53.000Z","uid":389,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e95a2c388b2dab421b82154d2002534933d8000f","tid":279703,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins1706111497172081321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins1706111497172081321&d=xdvyTn8elpyOrQjx963uTDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=cf465348\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins1706111497172081321&h=22c28e3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins1706111497172081321</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/211141_6e1fe34ceff88d5afb4d2ac9890729aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F211141_6e1fe34ceff88d5afb4d2ac9890729aa.jpg&h=8163fbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡名人仇思達昨晚於網台節目播出聲稱是熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰錄音，指青年新政梁頌恆、游蕙禎「應該死啦」，稱只是與兩人「扮friend」，又批評「大眾白癡」，以為他們是「本土派」。鄭松泰昨晚於facebook疑似回應事件，承認「內部工作組的話被流出」，並指摘「當日有份支持梁游而令教主黃毓民敗選的人，全部都是智力有問題」。 - See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170611/s00001/1497172081321#sthash.BAl21QpJ.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170611%2Fs00001%2F1497172081321%23sthash.BAl21QpJ.dpuf&d=xdvyTn8elpyOrQjx963uTDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=fd885cd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170611%2Fs00001%2F1497172081321%23sthash.BAl21QpJ.dpuf&h=a008f17d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170611/s00001/1497172081321#sthash.BAl21QpJ.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"962a3ee62a5676a073f427d70961d302dfef4305","tid":279703,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"每日新聞<br />\n即時新聞<br />\n <br />\n訂閱明報電子報<br />\n明報新聞網 明報AppiOS 明報AppAndroid 明報App<br />\n港聞 【內部錄音流出】鄭松泰指「大眾白癡」：以為我們是本土派　爆粗狂轟梁頌恆游蕙禎 (19:58)<br />\n2017/6/11<br />\n<br />\n 共1幅 下一頁 <br />\n網絡名人仇思達昨晚於網台節目播出聲稱是熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰錄音，指青年新政梁頌恆、游蕙禎「應該死啦」，稱只是與兩人「扮friend」，又批評「大眾白癡」，以為他們是「本土派」。鄭松泰昨晚於facebook疑似回應事件，承認「內部工作組的話被流出」，並指摘「當日有份支持梁游而令教主黃毓民敗選的人，全部都是智力有問題」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：林鄭質疑港獨是否成思潮 「僅小撮人不切實際言論」<br />\n<br />\n仇思達昨晚於網台節目播出、據稱是熱血公民議員鄭松泰錄音，有一把男聲說：「我想大家理解嘅就係，9月至到1、2月，梁頌恆、游蕙禎呢啲，X你，佢哋應該死啦X家鏟。但係問題係，我喺公眾場合我唔可以&hellip;&hellip;我要同佢哋扮friend，我要喺我立場上顯示到畀其他人知道我哋係幫緊佢哋，因為大眾白癡嘛，佢哋以為我哋係本土派！以為本土派係同一批人」"},{"pid":"c409d1cd2e930d3c614d092d2a33d473e5287a60","tid":279703,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:07:18.000Z","msg":"一係自爆一係假（佢自己放出嚟有目的，表忠）<br />\n何況一早唔當佢係，佢係大中華膠，泛民B隊嚟"},{"pid":"0212eeec5a70c4a82bb687bc6aab7a950bb4c5e0","tid":279703,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"咁背 尋晚節目 而家先出"},{"pid":"45904b1bb3038f8bf4a711a63032099e71f027b4","tid":279703,"uid":53735,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"講得好，選雞也不選教主是垃圾"},{"pid":"71816bfc0af0b9e5fb8fc39d86d75cb1c6b67977","tid":279703,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"無敵神駒就開心啦 搞下搞下真名又上報紙"},{"pid":"8117a3b8bdad9880eedc527cfa64d162ba398489","tid":279703,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無敵神駒就開心啦 搞下搞下真名又上報紙</blockquote><br />\n正白旗旗主重開心<br />\n<br />\n全世界白痴"},{"pid":"0447932713430be4f4ec9227d249419fc95323f9","tid":279703,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"其實想知神駒政治立場係咩，有邊個未俾佢屌過？"},{"pid":"0a9b3a4a772621ffbc49697bdd1752546211c45d","tid":279703,"uid":14449,"li